sentences: Daishi Dance (born Daishi Suzuki (鈴木大士, Suzuki Daishi) in 1976) is a male Japanese DJ and record producer.
Since March 2008, Daishi Dance has performed at the club ageHa, in Shinkiba, Tokyo at the regular party called "POOL HOUSE", and certain other events.
On July 2, 2008, Daishi Dance released "The Ghibli Set", which contained 12 licensed remixes songs featured in movies created by Studio Ghibli.
This album hit number 12 on the Oricon charts, and remained at this position for 3 weeks.
